3:T435,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"ProfessionalService","name":"Event Video & Conferences | I am Tomas","description":"Premium coverage for conferences and B2B events. CEO interviews, reports, and full recordings.","image":"https://en.jajsemtomas.cz/images/service-event.jpg","url":"https://en.jajsemtomas.cz/services/event-video","telephone":"+420732483004","email":"msg@jajsemtomas.cz","priceRange":"££","address":{"@type":"PostalAddress","addressLocality":"London","addressCountry":"UK"},"provider":{"@type":"Person","name":"Tomas Berka","url":"https://en.jajsemtomas.cz","jobTitle":"Video Producer & Filmmaker"},"areaServed":["London","United Kingdom","Europe"],"hasOfferCatalog":{"@type":"OfferCatalog","name":"Video Services","itemListElement":[{"@type":"Offer","itemOffered":{"@type":"Service","name":"Executive Interviews"}},{"@type":"Offer","itemOffered":{"@type":"Service","name":"Highlight Reels"}},{"@type":"Offer","itemOffered":{"@type":"Service","name":"Drone Footage"}},{"@type":"Offer","itemOffered":{"@type":"Service","name":"Express PR Delivery"}}]}}5:T8ab,<h2>Event Video That Works For You All Year</h2><p>You know how much you invest in organizing a conference — and how much of that disappears the day after? Professional event video turns that investment into <strong>an asset that sells for 12 months</strong>. It builds prestige, attracts sponsors, and drives registrations for next year.</p><h3>What I Capture</h3><ul><li><strong>Main stage</strong> — Keynotes, panel discussions, ceremonies. Multi-camera recording with professional audio</li><li><strong>CEO interviews</strong> — Short, engaging interviews with speakers and VIP guests. Perfect for LinkedIn</li><li><strong>Event atmosphere</strong> — Behind the scenes, networking, details. Content that shows the energy of your event</li><li><strong>Same-day highlights</strong> — Key moments edited and delivered the same day. For social media directly from the venue</li><li><strong>Attendee testimonials</strong> — Quick soundbites from guests that serve as social proof</li></ul><h3>Why B2B Companies Choose Me</h3><p>In corporate environments, <strong>discretion and professionalism</strong> are everything. I move discreetly among guests, never disturb speakers, and the output looks like a professional documentary — not an amateur vlog. I've filmed events for OICT, DEKRA, Tatra Trucks, and numerous conferences.</p><p>Through my partnership with <strong>SocialVids</strong>, we handle large international events with multi-person crews — 3+ cameras, livestream, drone, sound engineer.</p><h3>Indicative Pricing</h3><p><strong>BASIC (half day, 1 camera):</strong> from €750 — 3-5 min recap, delivery 7 days</p><p><strong>STANDARD (full day, 2 cameras):</strong> from €1,400 — 2 videos + interviews, delivery 5 days</p><p><strong>PREMIUM (multi-day, 3+ cameras):</strong> from €2,500 — Cinematic quality, livestream, 48h express</p><p><em>Prices are indicative and depend on specific requirements. <a href='/contact'>Request a quote</a> — I'll respond within 24 hours.</em></p><p><strong>Looking for international event coverage?</strong> See <a href='/services/international-event-video'>International Event Video</a> for city-specific pricing including London and Prague.</p>0:{"buildId":"IWoiNXIyNwXlhyWx9zoai","rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[["$","article",null,{"className":"py-20","children":[["$","$L2",null,{"items":[{"name":"Home","url":"https://en.jajsemtomas.cz"},{"name":"Services","url":"https://en.jajsemtomas.cz/#services"},{"name":"Event Video & Conferences","url":"https://en.jajsemtomas.cz/services/event-video"}]}],["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$3"}}],["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"FAQPage\",\"mainEntity\":[{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Do you film outside of London?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Yes, I film across the UK and internationally (primarily Prague).\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"How quickly will I receive the event video?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"I offer express delivery - short clips for social media the same evening, complete aftermovie within 5-7 days.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Do I need more videographers?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"For smaller events, I am enough. For large events, I can provide a full team.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Does the price include drone footage?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Drone footage is for an extra fee. We'll discuss this during the consultation.\"}}]}"}}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mx-auto w-full max-w-7xl px-4 md:px-6 lg:px-8","children":[["$","$L4",null,{"href":"/#services","className":"inline-flex items-center text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-primary mb-8 transition-colors","children":[["$","svg",null,{"xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","width":24,"height":24,"viewBox":"0 0 24 24","fill":"none","stroke":"currentColor","strokeWidth":2,"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","className":"lucide lucide-arrow-left h-4 w-4 mr-2","aria-hidden":"true","children":[["$","path","1l729n",{"d":"m12 19-7-7 7-7"}],["$","path","x3x0zl",{"d":"M19 12H5"}],"$undefined"]}]," Back to services"]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-16","children":[["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","h1",null,{"className":"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6","children":"Event Video & Conferences"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-xl text-muted-foreground mb-8 text-pretty","children":"Premium coverage for conferences and B2B events. CEO interviews, reports, and full recordings."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-invert prose-p:text-muted-foreground prose-p:leading-relaxed prose-strong:text-foreground mb-8 text-base","dangerouslySetInnerHT